.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-HTLC-MIN-SKEWNESS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-htlc-min-skewness \- FEAT-3620 channel-htlc-min-skewness
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-htlc-min-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the skewness of htlc_minimum_msat across all peer channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-3620).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBhtlc_min_skewness_msat\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
